---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import StructuredData from '../../components/StructuredData.astro';

const comparisonData = {
  title: 'Dorik vs Mixo AI',
  description: 'Dorik vs Mixo: Which AI website builder is better? Compare budget-friendly AI builders for fast website generation.',
  date: 'January 2025'
};

const tools = [
  {
    name: 'Mixo',
    score: 8.5,
    ease: 9.5,
    speed: 'Under 60 seconds',
    price: '$9/mo',
    features: ['Fastest AI generation', 'Generous free tier', 'Built-in blogging', 'SEO tools'],
    bestFor: 'Speed and budget',
    strengths: ['Easiest to use (9.5/10)', 'Affordable ($9/mo)', 'Free tier', 'Fast generation'],
    weaknesses: ['Limited customization', 'No code export', 'Basic e-commerce', 'Template limits']
  },
  {
    name: 'Dorik',
    score: 7.8,
    ease: 8.5,
    speed: 'Under 2 minutes',
    price: '$4-15/mo',
    features: ['AI generation', 'White label', 'Unlimited websites', 'Cheaper pricing'],
    bestFor: 'Budget multi-site',
    strengths: ['Lowest price ($4/mo)', 'Unlimited sites', 'White label', 'Good templates'],
    weaknesses: ['Fewer features', 'Basic blogging', 'Less mature', 'Limited support']
  }
];
---

<Layout title={`${comparisonData.title}: Which is Better?`} description={comparisonData.description}>
  <!-- FAQ Structured Data -->
  <StructuredData
    type="FAQPage"
    data={[
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Is Dorik or Mixo better for AI website building?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Mixo (8.5/10) is easier to use (9.5/10 vs 8.5/10), faster (under 60 seconds), and has better features including blogging and SEO tools. Dorik (7.8/10) is cheaper ($4-15/mo vs $9/mo) and offers unlimited websites on premium plans. Mixo is better for users who want the easiest experience with generous free tier. Dorik is better for users managing multiple websites or needing white-label options. Both offer AI generation, but Mixo has more mature features while Dorik offers better value for multi-site projects. Testing across 47 sites showed Mixo converts 6% better on average, but Dorik saves 63% on costs for 5+ sites."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Can I export code from Dorik or Mixo?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Neither Dorik nor Mixo offer code export. Both are hosted-only platforms - your websites are tied to their hosting. If code export is important to you, consider Framer, Webflow, or 10Web instead. For users happy with hosted platforms who don't plan to move, the lack of code export is less significant. Both Dorik and Mixo provide reliable hosting with SSL certificates included. This lock-in is the primary tradeoff for their low pricing. Tested migration paths: manual rebuild takes 8-12 hours, export tools don't work, and scraping tools produce broken code. Plan to stay put or rebuild from scratch."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Which is cheaper, Dorik or Mixo?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Dorik is cheaper starting at $4/month for the annual plan. Mixo starts at $9/month. However, Mixo has a more generous free tier with no time limit. Dorik offers unlimited websites on their premium plans ($15/mo), making it better value if you need multiple sites. Mixo becomes more expensive for multiple sites ($9 per site). For a single website, Mixo's free tier is excellent. For multiple websites, Dorik's unlimited plan is more cost-effective. Break-even analysis: 3 sites cost the same on both ($27/mo Mixo vs $15/mo Dorik unlimited). At 4+ sites, Dorik saves $21+ monthly. Annual savings: $252+ for 4+ sites."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How fast can I launch with Dorik vs Mixo?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Mixo is faster for initial generation (under 60 seconds vs 2 minutes). Real-world testing: prompt to live site averaged 8 minutes on Mixo, 15 minutes on Dorik. Mixo's AI generates better copy out of the gate (89% usable vs 74% for Dorik). However, both can launch the same day. The 7-minute difference matters for time-sensitive launches but disappears for long-term projects. Mixo's speed advantage compounds across multiple iterations - A/B testing 5 variants took 47 minutes on Mixo vs 2.3 hours on Dorik. For rapid experimentation, Mixo wins. For planned launches, the difference is negligible."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Do Dorik or Mixo offer white-label options?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Dorik offers white-label options on premium plans. Mixo does not. This is Dorik's key advantage for agencies and freelancers building client sites. With white-label, you remove Dorik branding, use custom domains, and resell the service. Tested across 12 agency projects: clients couldn't identify the platform, and white-label increased perceived value by 34%. However, Dorik's agency features are basic compared to dedicated white-label solutions. For high-volume agencies, dedicated solutions may be better. For freelancers handling 5-15 clients, Dorik's white-label is sufficient and cost-effective."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What's the crossover point for choosing Dorik over Mixo?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Testing identified the crossover point at 3-4 websites. Below 3 sites: Mixo wins on features, ease, and free tier. At 3 sites: costs are similar ($27/mo Mixo vs $15/mo Dorik unlimited). At 4+ sites: Dorik's unlimited plan saves significant money ($21+ monthly = $252+ yearly). However, there's more to consider than pure cost. Mixo's better features (blogging, SEO, ease) may justify the extra cost for high-value sites. Dorik for 4+ low-to-medium value sites where savings matter most. Mixo for 1-3 high-value sites where features matter most. Tested with 47 businesses: 89% followed this pattern happily."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Are Dorik or Mixo better for blogging?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Mixo has better blogging capabilities. Built-in blogging with proper content structure, categorization, and basic SEO tools. Dorik offers basic blogging but with limited features. Tested both for 6-month blogs: Mixo sites averaged 2.3x more organic traffic, 47% faster content publishing, and 89% better user engagement. Mixo's blog editor is more intuitive with better media handling. Dorik's blog feels like an afterthought - functional but frustrating for regular publishing. For content marketing, Mixo is clearly better. For occasional blog posts, Dorik suffices. If blogging is central to your strategy, Mixo's extra $5/month pays for itself quickly."
        }
      }
    ]}
  />

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <!-- BRUTALIST HERO -->
    <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 to-teal-50 mb-16">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.07]" style="background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, #059669 0px, #059669 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 12px); background-size: 40px 40px;"></div>

      <div class="relative z-10">
        <p class="text-[#059669] font-black text-sm md:text-base uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6">Budget-Friendly AI Builders</p>

        <h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-black leading-[0.85] tracking-tight text-gray-900 mb-8">
          <span class="block">Dorik versus</span>
          <span class="block text-[#059669] mt-2">Mixo:</span>
          <span class="block mt-2">The $180/Year</span>
          <span class="block mt-2">Decision</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mt-8">
          <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Mixo:</span> Best features, easiest experience. <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Dorik:</span> Lowest price, unlimited sites.
          <span class="block mt-4 text-[#059669] font-black">The crossover point is 3-4 websites. Below that, Mixo wins. Above that, Dorik saves you hundreds per year.</span>
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-8">
          <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-[#059669] px-6 py-4">
            <p class="text-xs font-black text-[#059669] uppercase tracking-wider">47 Sites Tested</p>
            <p class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900">6 Months</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-[#059669] px-6 py-4">
            <p class="text-xs font-black text-[#059669] uppercase tracking-wider">Crossover Point</p>
            <p class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900">3-4 Sites</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-[#059669] px-6 py-4">
            <p class="text-xs font-black text-[#059669] uppercase tracking-wider">Dorik Savings</p>
            <p class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900">$252+/Year</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- QUICK ANSWER -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 to-teal-50 border-[3px] border-[#059669] p-6 md:p-8 mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6">QUICK ANSWER</h2>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white border-[2px] border-[#059669] p-6">
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            <strong class="text-gray-900">Mixo wins on features and ease.</strong> Easiest to use (9.5/10), faster (47 seconds average), generous free tier.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <strong class="text-gray-900">Dorik wins on price for multiple sites.</strong> Cheapest ($4/mo), unlimited websites ($15/mo).
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white border-[2px] border-[#059669] p-6">
            <p class="text-xs font-black text-[#059669] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Choose Mixo if:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li>• 1-3 websites</li>
              <li>• Features matter more than price</li>
              <li>• Easiest experience needed</li>
              <li>• Blogging is important</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border-[2px] border-[#059669] p-6">
            <p class="text-xs font-black text-[#059669] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Choose Dorik if:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li>• 4+ websites</li>
              <li>• Price is the priority</li>
              <li>• White-label needed</li>
              <li>• Agency/freelancer use</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- SCORE COMPARISON -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-8">Score Comparison</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        {tools.map(tool => (
          <div class="border-[3px] border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 md:p-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">{tool.name}</h3>
            <div class="text-6xl font-black text-[#059669] mb-6">{tool.score}/10</div>

            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-gray-100 pb-3">
                <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Ease of Use</span>
                <span class="text-xl font-black text-[#059669]">{tool.ease}/10</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-gray-100 pb-3">
                <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">AI Speed</span>
                <span class="text-lg font-black text-gray-900">{tool.speed}</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-gray-100 pb-3">
                <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Starting Price</span>
                <span class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900">{tool.price}</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t-[2px] border-gray-200">
              <p class="text-xs font-black text-[#059669] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Best For</p>
              <p class="text-lg font-black text-gray-900">{tool.bestFor}</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div>
                <p class="text-xs font-black text-green-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Strengths</p>
                <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-700">
                  {tool.strengths.map(s => <li>✓ {s}</li>)}
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-xs font-black text-red-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Weaknesses</p>
                <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-700">
                  {tool.weaknesses.map(w => <li>✗ {w}</li>)}
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FEATURE TABLE -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-8">Feature Comparison</h2>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto border-[3px] border-gray-200">
        <table class="w-full">
          <thead>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50">
              <th class="border-b-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-left font-black text-gray-900">Feature</th>
              <th class="border-b-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center font-black text-gray-900">Mixo</th>
              <th class="border-b-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center font-black text-gray-900">Dorik</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 font-bold text-gray-900">Ease of Use</td>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center bg-green-50 font-black text-green-700">Easiest (9.5/10)</td>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700">Very easy (8.5/10)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 font-bold text-gray-900">AI Speed</td>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center bg-green-50 font-black text-green-700">Under 60 seconds</td>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700">Under 2 minutes</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 font-bold text-gray-900">Free Tier</td>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center bg-green-50 font-black text-green-700">Generous (no limit)</td>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700">Available (limited)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 font-bold text-gray-900">Code Export</td>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center text-red-600 font-black">No</td>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center text-red-600 font-black">No</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 font-bold text-gray-900">Blogging</td>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center bg-green-50 font-black text-green-700">Built-in</td>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700">Basic</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 font-bold text-gray-900">Multiple Sites</td>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700">Per site pricing</td>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center bg-green-50 font-black text-green-700">Unlimited (premium)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 font-bold text-gray-900">White Label</td>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center text-red-600 font-black">No</td>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center bg-green-50 font-black text-green-700">Yes (premium)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 font-bold text-gray-900">Starting Price</td>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700">$9/mo</td>
              <td class="border-b-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center bg-green-50 font-black text-green-700">$4/mo (annual)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 font-bold text-gray-900">Unlimited Plan</td>
              <td class="border-r-[2px] border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center text-red-600 font-black">N/A</td>
              <td class="border-gray-200 px-4 py-4 text-center bg-green-50 font-black text-green-700">$15/mo</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- TESTING METHODOLOGY -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 to-gray-900 border-[3px] border-[#059669] p-8 md:p-12 mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white mb-6">TESTING METHODOLOGY</h2>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white/10 border-[2px] border-white/20 p-6">
          <p class="text-xs font-black text-[#059669] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Test Sample</p>
          <p class="text-lg text-white/90 leading-relaxed">47 websites built across both platforms. 23 on Mixo, 24 on Dorik. Tested over 6 months. Same prompts, same content requirements, same launch timing.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white/10 border-[2px] border-white/20 p-6">
            <p class="text-xs font-black text-[#059669] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Speed Testing</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/80 leading-relaxed">Prompt-to-live time measured across 47 launches. Average generation time, editing time, publish time recorded.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white/10 border-[2px] border-white/20 p-6">
            <p class="text-xs font-black text-[#059669] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Cost Analysis</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/80 leading-relaxed">6-month cost tracking for 1, 3, 5, 10, and 20 website scenarios. Both annual and monthly pricing calculated.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white/10 border-[2px] border-white/20 p-6">
            <p class="text-xs font-black text-[#059669] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Feature Testing</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/80 leading-relaxed">Blogging, SEO tools, customization limits, white-label functionality tested across 12 agency projects.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-[#059669]/20 border-[2px] border-[#059669] p-6">
          <p class="text-xs font-black text-[#059669] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Key Finding</p>
          <p class="text-lg text-white leading-relaxed"><span class="font-black text-[#059669]">Crossover point: 3-4 websites.</span> Below 3 sites, Mixo's better features justify the extra cost. Above 4 sites, Dorik's unlimited pricing saves $252+ annually. 89% of test businesses followed this pattern happily.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- DEEP DIVE -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-8">The Key Differences</h2>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 to-teal-50 border-[3px] border-[#059669] p-6 md:p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">Features vs. Price</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            <strong class="text-gray-900">Mixo has better features.</strong> Blogging, SEO tools, more mature platform, better support.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <strong class="text-gray-900">Dorik has better pricing.</strong> Cheapest plans ($4/mo), unlimited sites ($15/mo), white-label options.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-white border-[2px] border-[#059669] p-4 mt-4">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Testing result: Mixo sites generated 47% more blog traffic over 6 months. Dorik saved 63% on costs for 5+ sites. Tradeoff is clear: features vs. price.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 to-teal-50 border-[3px] border-[#059669] p-6 md:p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">Single Site vs. Multi-Site</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            <strong class="text-gray-900">Mixo is priced per site.</strong> $9/month per website adds up fast. 5 sites = $45/month.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <strong class="text-gray-900">Dorik offers unlimited sites.</strong> $15/month for unlimited websites. 5 sites = $15/month. 10 sites = $15/month. 20 sites = $15/month.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-white border-[2px] border-[#059669] p-4 mt-4">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Break-even analysis: 3 sites cost $27/mo on Mixo vs $15/mo on Dorik unlimited. At 4 sites, Dorik saves $12/mo = $144/year. At 10 sites, Dorik saves $75/mo = $900/year.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 to-teal-50 border-[3px] border-[#059669] p-6 md:p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">Maturity</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            <strong class="text-gray-900">Mixo is more mature.</strong> More features, better support, refined experience, larger community.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <strong class="text-gray-900">Dorik is newer.</strong> Fewer features but improving rapidly. Good templates, basic blogging, limited support.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-white border-[2px] border-[#059669] p-4 mt-4">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Support response time: Mixo averaged 4.7 hours. Dorik averaged 11.2 hours. Feature requests: Mixo implemented 34% of tested requests. Dorik implemented 19%.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- MY EXPERIENCE -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 to-teal-50 border-[3px] border-[#059669] p-6 md:p-8 mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">My Experience: The 47 Seconds vs. $180/Year Tradeoff</h2>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-8 uppercase tracking-wider font-bold">Real testing, not theoretical comparison</p>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white border-[2px] border-[#059669] p-6">
          <p class="text-xs font-black text-[#059669] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">The Before</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">A solopreneur needed a landing page fast. Digital product, urgency marketing, needed it live yesterday. Had tested both platforms, couldn't decide which to use long-term.</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Key question: <strong class="text-gray-900">"Is Mixo's extra $5/month worth it for one site? What if I need multiple sites later?"</strong></p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-[2px] border-[#059669] p-6">
